posting_body: ['Bright 1 Bedroom In The Heart of Eastlake- 2 Weeks Free!', 'Property Address', 'The Bronz - 6 | 2046 Franklin Ave E | SEattle, WA 98102', 'Available: Now', 'Offered By', 'Seattle Property Management Assoc, LLC', 'Description', "The Bronz is a charming 12 unit building located in the heart of Eastlake just one block from the popular Sarafina Restaurant, and a few blocks to the popular Pete's Market and Grand Central Bakery, as well as all of the other great shops along Eastlake.", 'We are offering this bright-light filled 1 bedroom apartment on a 12 month Lease Term with 2 Weeks Free Rent.', ' At the time of application we require payment of the $25 application fee per person and a $1000 deposit that is then applied to the refundable security deposit upon approval.', ' This building is non-smoking.', ' Cats are allowed.', ' sorry, no dogs.', 'The monthly rent is $1850 and there is a $75 per month utility fee.', 'For more information, please call Ryan at', 'show contact info', 'Please visit our website to see a complete list of available units <URL>', 'Amenities', 'Small Building', 'Controlled Access', 'Wood Floors', 'Vaulted Ceiling', 'Small Deck', 'Laundry On Site', 'near transportation', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 1BD/1.0BA', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $1,850.00', 'Available: Now', 'Application Fee: $25.00', 'Security Deposit: $1,000.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed', 'Dogs not allowed']
